### Get My User
@authToken = 
GET https://localhost:8443/api/qry/user/me HTTP/1.1
accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
X-API-Version: 1



### Get User by Entity Key
GET https://localhost:8443/api/qry/user?entityKey=3ctn0Jm&size=lg HTTP/1.1
accept: application/json
X-API-Version: 1


### Check if username exists (should return true if user was created above)
GET https://localhost:8443/api/qry/user/check-username?username=johndoe123 HTTP/1.1
accept: application/json
X-API-Version: 1


### Check if username exists (should return false for non-existing user)
GET https://localhost:8443/api/qry/user/check-username?username=nonexistentuser HTTP/1.1
accept: application/json
X-API-Version: 1


### Check if email exists (should return true if user was created above)
GET https://localhost:8443/api/qry/user/check-email?email=john.doe@example.com HTTP/1.1
accept: application/json
X-API-Version: 1


### Check if email exists (should return false for non-existing email)
GET https://localhost:8443/api/qry/user/check-email?email=nonexistent@example.com HTTP/1.1
accept: application/json
X-API-Version: 1

